{"tid":1550482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔用八達通可以去邊度換番啲神沙番嚟?","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:22.000Z","uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c860ed51ea9a328965987e77466876de00d90a8","tid":1550482,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"想呼應吓罷用八達通<br />\n最近都係用神沙搭巴士<br />\n但屋企啲神沙都清得七七八八<br />\n而除咗搭車又已經無乜地方會找毫子<br />\n<br />\n可以有咩方法換堆神沙番嚟?"},{"pid":"036cdd8ae96266a4aad44228e739407d55a53635","tid":1550482,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c0453c3fc46dfd300cc1a5136dc68266cf4cc01","tid":1550482,"uid":282289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n百佳<br />\n街市阿嬸"},{"pid":"22660e46aa164b2640654c8151053dd2f8943033","tid":1550482,"uid":167802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c0453c3fc46dfd300cc1a5136dc68266cf4cc01","tid":1550482,"uid":282289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n百佳<br />\n街市阿嬸"},"citedBy":